Sabre easily dodge. "Wing look out?!" But alas she was tangled in the 
fight with the other Eagle and she was hit between the 
wings. "Sqwark!" She began to nose dive to the ground...

Rave cried out firing over and over at Starstorm with his stun 
blasters, NightViper reared before windlord. "Ssso nice to meet you, 
letsss do lunch." He smiled. "NightViper... TERRORIZE!" Transforming 
he became the large KingCobra and lunged at the Hawk.

Sabre turned and with one quick throw threw the sword blade first at 
Starstorm's wing...
